snippet.title: CGDC Community Game DaN Project March 2021  Update
snippet.description:
In the month of March, we have finally started pulling together some of the final strings in art, music, story, and development. We have a cool song to share, as well as some audio from our cutscenes. Soon, we hope to have a full cutscene to share!

Sign up for our newsletter and become a beta tester!
https://docs.google.com/forms/d/1Kezzmk_tvkyPM_VBFakv8XSI68F4Eky_ECRgdE4w2Vo/edit?usp=sharing
